First Lady Michelle Obama will be participating in The United State of Women Summit, where she will join Oprah Winfrey for a conversation about empowering women and inspiring the next generation. The summit will address various topics including gender equality, economic empowerment, health and wellness, education, violence, entrepreneurship, and leadership. Later in the evening, the First Lady will deliver remarks at The United State of Women Dinner, which will focus on women's economic empowerment and the Let Girls Learn initiative.